column5: Hey Pete I hope your having a great day today.  See ya next weekend
Happy Birthday Pete
Happy Birthday Hon!!!  Hope you're having a super day
have a great one Pete!
Happy Birthday to you Pete!
All the best pal, from both me & the Mrs.
A great day I hope Peter !!
Happy B-day Pete, next Saturday would be a great day to buy yourself a nice b-day present!
Have a great b-day Pete!
Thanks Gang!! Just throwing the 2 lb lobsters in the water and getting the steaks ready for the BBQ!! Gonna be awesome!!!
Have a good B day Pete all the best to you.   Art
Happy BDAY Pete.  Enjoy yer day.
All the best for your birthday Pete...
Happy birthday big guy!!!
Thanks guys, the lobster was awesome!
I'll bet! Just like I'll bet my invite to dinner is lost in the mail.....  Hope it was awesome Pete.
Happy Belated Birfday, Hon.  No, wait, I meant HB to you, Pete.  Best wishes to you and your family.
HAPPY BIRTHDAY PETE that's such a cool name
Amen!!
Actually one of my best friends that I grew up was named Amen....   Art
Yes .. Happy belated  I actually got Squidman.com reserved a number of years back ... thats what people who confused Calamari with my last name used to call me
